## packer.nvim
The vim dot files make use of the excellent [packer.nvim](https://github.com/wbthomason/packer.nvim) Vim plugin manager.

`packer.nvim` will be automatically setup for you. Just run `:PackerInstall` in nvim to install the plugins on first start.

